The Tokai Bank Ltd, London Branch, isdoubling the size of a sterling certificate of deposit issuancefacility established last year to 200 mln stg from the original100 mln, Chemical Bank International Ltd said as arranger.    The increase reflects active use of the facility from thefirst month after signing and growing international interestfrom institutional investors at sub-LIBOR (London InterbankOffered Rates) levels.    Barclay's de Zoete Wedd Ltd has been added to the group ofdealers for the program. REUTER&#3;